I've uploaded zipped folders and md5 cehcksums to Google Drive, which was then backed up to my SIFP_2025/CloudSync_deposit folder on Gannet via CloudSync. I then moved the files from the CloudSync_deposit folder up to just the SIFP_2025 folder manually in the Gannet file manager.

Now, check checksums (doing this via ssh into Gannet, but copying here for record)

```{r, engine='bash', eval=FALSE}

kdurkin1@Gannet:/volume2/web/kdurkin1/SIFP_2025$ md5sum Group2_L3_Flongle.zip
# ba0b938cb6c429f9ca873e779d5d8439  Group2_L3_Flongle.zip
```
